This delicious vanilla cake is made up of several layers glazed with homemade caramel and finished off with a delectable buttercream frosting. If you are celebrating a birthday, this vanilla cake would make for the perfect birthday treat, or you can wow your guests with this mouth-watering dessert after Sunday lunch. ALSO SEE: Recipe of the day: Deliciously sweet banana cream meringue For the caramel sauce (used as glaze and in frosting) For the caramel buttercream frosting ALSO SEE: Saturday tasty treat: Honey butter potato chips For the caramel sauce For the caramel buttercream Assemble the cake *This recipe was found on mycakeschool.com.